@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Quản trị viên" as User #Yellow
boundary "CustomerDetailPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as MW #Yellow
control "CustomersController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "CustomerService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Customer" as CEnt #Yellow
entity "Booking" as BEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Click vào một người dùng
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Lấy customerId từ route params
UI -> API : 1.2: GET /api/Customers/{id}\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer {token}
activate API

API -> API : 1.3: Axios interceptor: gắn Bearer token
API -> MW : 1.4: Request qua JwtMiddleware
activate MW
MW -> MW : 1.5: ValidateToken
alt 1.6: [Token không hợp lệ]
MW --> API : 1.6.1: 401
API --> UI : 1.6.2: Redirect login
else 1.7: [Token hợp lệ]
MW --> Ctrl : 1.7.1: Chuyển tiếp
deactivate MW

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.8: GetByIdAsync(id)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.9: Customers.GetQueryable()\n.Include(c => c.Bookings)\n.FirstOrDefaultAsync(c => c.Id == id)
activate DB

alt 1.10: [Customer không tồn tại]
DB --> Svc : 1.10.1: null
deactivate DB
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.10.2: ApiResponse.Fail("Customer not found", 404)
Ctrl --> API : 1.10.3: 404
API --> UI : 1.10.4: Lỗi
UI --> User : 1.10.5: "Customer not found"
else 1.11: [Customer tồn tại]
DB --> Svc : 1.11.1: Customer (có Bookings)
deactivate DB
Svc -> Svc : 1.11.2: _mapper.Map<CustomerResponse>(customer)\n(BookingCount = Bookings.Count)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.11.3: ApiResponse.Ok(data)
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.12: 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.13: Response JSON chi tiết
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.14: Hiển thị:\n- Thông tin cá nhân (họ tên, email,\nphone, địa chỉ, passport...)\n- Số lượng booking\n- Lịch sử giao dịch
UI --> User : 1.15: Xem thông tin chi tiết
deactivate UI

@enduml
